Device Specifications in Labs

Normal Labs

  • Desktop PCs with Intel i5 processors, 8GB RAM, 500GB SSD
  • Windows 10 operating system
  • Basic software: MS Office Suite, Visual Studio Code, MATLAB

Specialized Labs

  • High-end Workstations with Intel i7 processors, 16GB RAM, 1TB SSD
  • Dual boot with Windows 10 and Ubuntu Linux
  • Advanced software: AutoCAD, SolidWorks, MATLAB, Packet Tracer

Mac Lab

  • iMacs with M1 Chip, 16GB RAM, 512GB SSD
  • macOS operating system
  • Software: Xcode, Adobe Creative Suite, Final Cut Pro, Logic Pro

Available Software

Networking and Simulation

  • Cisco Packet Tracer
  • GNS3
  • VMware Workstation

Operating Systems

  • Windows 10
  • Ubuntu Linux
  • macOS

Programming and Development

  • Visual Studio Code
  • PyCharm
  • Eclipse IDE
  • Xcode (Mac Lab)

Virtualization

  • VMware Workstation
  • VirtualBox
  • Hyper-V
); }; export default Specifications;
